Program: The Why Factor
Title: Why Do We Make Lists?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p04krtz7
Last Broadcast Date: Christmas Day 2016
Lists of things to do and things to buy. Presents we want for Christmas, or things we desire in a lover. Lists help us organise our thoughts and bring order to a confusing world. But what do they reveal about us? (Photo: An original Madonna handwriten 1990 'to do' diary. Credit: Henry S. Dziekan III/Getty Images) Show less